# WHY .dockerignore: Prevents unnecessary files from being sent
# to the Docker build context. Without this, node_modules, bin, obj,
# and .git directories bloat every build — slowing down CI/CD pipelines.

**/.git
**/.vs
**/.idea
**/bin
**/obj
**/*.user
**/*.suo
**/Dockerfile*
**/.dockerignore
**/README.md
**/launchSettings.json